parameters.name: objectId
parameters.description: The {objectName} Id. You can find the key(s) required in the `GET /objects/{objectName}/metadata` call, indicated by the 'primaryKey' attribute. Note: `objectId` is typically a composite key, i.e., to delete SalesAgreementLines objectId you should enter: `LineNumber=1,SalesAgreementId='SAG-000001',dataAreaId='usmf' `
